d:X\times X \to\mathbb{R}
X
X
d(x,y)=d(y,x)\ \forall x,y\in X\tag{*}
(*)
X=\{a,b\}
d
d(a,a)=d(b,b)=0
d(a,b)=1, d(b,a)=2
d
(*)
\mathbb{R}
\delta(x,y)= \left\{ \begin{array}{cl} |x-y| & \text{if} \ x \leq y \\ \frac{1}{2}|x-y| & \text{if} \ x>y \end{array} \right. .
\delta(x,y)=0
x=y
\delta(x,y) \leq \delta(x,z)+\delta(z,y)
\delta(x,y)= \delta(y,x)
x=y
